Text:
Reggie is the seventh studio album by rapper Redman. It is scheduled to be released 
on October 19, 2010. The original title of the album, as promoted in the booklet of Blackout! II, 
was going to be Reggie Noble "0" 9 1/2... So i hope you all like this Cd...
